Privacy Policy for EVIT Smart Charger Alexa Skill

Last updated: 30 Jan, 2026

This Alexa Skill (“EVIT Smart Charger”) is provided by EVIT.

Data Collection and Usage
This skill requires account linking to connect your Alexa account with your EVIT charger account. During use, the skill may access and process the following information:

• EVIT account identifier used for authentication
• EVIT charger information such as charger name, status, and charging state
• User-issued commands such as starting or stopping charging

The skill does NOT collect or store:
• Alexa voice recordings
• Personal Alexa profile data
• Payment or billing information

Purpose of Data Usage
The data is used only to:
• Authenticate EVIT users
• Identify EVIT chargers linked to the user
• Execute user-requested charger actions
• Provide spoken responses about charger status

Data Sharing
User data is not shared with third parties and is used solely for operating EVIT charger services.

Data Retention
Authentication tokens are stored securely and expire automatically. Charger data is retained only as required to provide the service.

Security
EVIT uses industry-standard security measures, including encrypted communication and access control.

User Control
Users can disable the skill at any time through the Alexa app, which immediately stops access.

Contact
Email: harshit@evitpl.com
